OL,3,CFree abortions 'risks' them being form
OL,4,Cof contraception, health boss says
OL,6,FSpeaking at a Health and Social
OL,7,FSecurity Panel on Tuesday (10
OL,8,FFebruary), she suggested that a
OL,9,Fminority of people on the island
OL,10,Falready choose to have abortions ahead
OL,11,Fof other treatment options.
OL,13,F"There is quite a lot of information
OL,14,Fand research showing there is a very
OL,15,Fsmall, but core, group of women who
OL,16,Fuse terminations as a form of
OL,17,Fcontraception, because of barriers to
OL,18,Faccessing contraception," said Ms
OL,19,FJohnson.
