OL,3,CFree abortions 'risks' them being form
OL,4,Cof contraception, health boss says
OL,6,F"In Jersey, contraception is a paid-
OL,7,Ffor service, and if termination was to
OL,8,Fbe made free, you run the risk of
OL,9,Fcreating perverse incentives to use
OL,10,Fearly-stage termination as a form of
OL,11,Fcontraception.
OL,13,F"So, if we were to think about
OL,14,Ftermination as a wholly free service,
OL,15,Fwe would need to think about what
OL,16,Fhappens to access to contraception as
OL,17,Fwell, from a public policy
OL,18,Fperspective."
