OL,3,CFree abortions 'risks' them being form
OL,4,Cof contraception, health boss says
OL,6,FIn Jersey, female contraception can
OL,7,Fcost anywhere between #17 for a
OL,8,Fmonth's supply of contraceptive pills,
OL,9,Fincluding an attendance fee at a
OL,10,Fclinic, to as much as #125 for
OL,11,Finserting a contraceptive implant or a
OL,12,Fcoil.
OL,14,FCondoms, however, are free if
OL,15,Fcollected from sexual health clinics.
OL,17,FAn abortion in Jersey costs #185 for
OL,18,Fanyone who has been a resident on the
OL,19,Fisland for six months or more, or #511
OL,20,Fif someone has lived there for less
OL,21,Ftime. However, there are exemptions.
