OL,3,CFree abortions 'risks' them being form
OL,4,Cof contraception, health boss says
OL,6,F"I personally believe contraception
OL,7,Fshould be free and easy to access. My
OL,8,Fpanel strongly believes that the next
OL,9,FHealth Minister needs to prioritise
OL,10,Fthis urgently."
OL,12,FIn the UK, all male and female
OL,13,Fcontraception is freely available on
OL,14,Fthe NHS.
OL,16,FSimilarly, almost all abortions are
OL,17,Ffree for anyone eligible for NHS care.
